Package com.sicomsa.dmt

Class VerificaResponse

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.SatResponse
com.sicomsa.dmt.VerificaResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class VerificaResponse extends SatResponse
VerificaResponse is SAT's response from a "verify download request" made to the massive download web service when requesting a verification for a particular request mapped by a requestId or (IdSolicitud) provided in a download request of a particular query.
Since:
1.0
Version:
2025.01.04
Author:
Beto Lopez

    • VerificaResponse

      public VerificaResponse(Instant satInstant, String statusCode, String message, int state, String solicitudeSts, String requestId)
      Returns a VerificaResponse with the given parameters. It is recommended to use the VerificaResponse.Builder class to instantiate this class.
      Parameters:
      satInstant - Instant mesage was received from SAT
      statusCode - status code of the received message
      message - message received
      state - state of the request
      solicitudeSts - status code of the download request
      requestId - request if of the download request
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if satInstant is null

    • VerificaResponse

      public VerificaResponse(Instant satInstant, String statusCode, String message, int solicitudeState, String solicitudeStsCode, String requestId, int cfdis, PackageIds packageIds)
      Returns a VerificaResponse with the given parameters. It is recommended to use the VerificaResponse.Builder class to instantiate this class.

      solicitudeStsCode - status code of the download request
